OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstay, say managers         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Working from home for part of the week 
OL,6, has become the norm for some employees,
OL,7, a survey of managers has suggested.    
OL,9,FMore than 80% said their firms had     
OL,10,Fadopted hybrid working - most since the
OL,11,Fpandemic, a survey for the Chartered   
OL,12,FInstitute of Management (CMI) found.   
OL,14,FBut senior leaders are also actively   
OL,15,Fencouraging employees to return to the 
OL,16,Fworkplace, a majority of managers said.
OL,18,FThe institute said firms should embrace
OL,19,Fhybrid work as "best practice".        
